<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[slice aubergines lengthways 2cm thick 4 cm long]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[deep fry in oil 3m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[if using tofu: cut in 4cm sticks, optionaly roll in cornstarch, deep fry too]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[chop garlic, ginger, slice chillies in rings]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[heat stock so it's warm]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[discard oil, except for 1 tbsp, then stir fry garlic, ginger, chilies a fes sc]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add the chilli bean paste and aubergines and tofu if using]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add host stock (5) and bring to boil; then heat down and 3m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add soy sauce, vinegar, sugar, few secs]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add cornstarch to thicken sauce]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[garnish with chopped spring onion]]></step>
</directions>
